# Summary
The Braze (Event Stream) destination integration enables real-time forwarding of Amplitude events and user data to Braze, requiring Braze API credentials and configuration of user ID mappings, event filtering, and property selection to power personalized customer engagement across channels.

# Keywords
- Braze API Endpoint
- External ID/Braze ID/User Alias mapping
- Event streaming configuration
- User property forwarding
- Custom event properties
- Update Users Only option
- User identification methods
- Bidirectional data flow